channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i59.tinypic.com/rszskk.png[/img][/center] [center]Allow me to welcome you all to this thread that will give you a little in site on Exfaction, firstly (you can skip this part if you prefer to look at pictures ;)) Exfaction is a 742 server loading 747 items models. We are a new server that is always updating to give you the players more content and excitement. I wont give away to many spoilers because that's what the pictures are for but, if you like the look of Exfaction please use the following links to come and join our newly formed community :)
Website = http://www.exfaction.org Forums = http://www.exfaction.org/mybb/[/center] Exfactions home (showing off some armour too ;)) [spoiler][IMG]http://i62.tinypic.com/9qiu10.png[/img][/spoiler] Extreme Donator Area (Located in Enchanted Vally) [spoiler][IMG]http://i60.tinypic.com/rjnq81.png[/img][/spoiler] Extreme Donator Area (still being working on, we could use some ideas :)) [spoiler][IMG]http://i60.tinypic.com/25frnee.png[/img][/spoiler] Donatorzone [spoiler][IMG]http://i60.tinypic.com/n6ddfb.png[/img][/spoiler] Shows New god wars map data (also showing off an armour set to make this picture more interesting ;)) [spoiler][IMG]http://i59.tinypic.com/iviebo.png[/img][/spoiler]
[center]The pictures above only show a fraction of what Exfaction is all about, to find out more come and visit us today, what are you waiting for?!?

Contact us 24 hours! (The contact us form goes to an E-mail which the staff team have linked on there phones for notifications) Skilling Easy and convenient teleporting for all Bossing and fun events :) High Combat xp Rates and lower skilling rates (because we encourage pkers to join :D and skilling is a choice ;)) And A lot more stuff not mentioned along with A lot more stuff to come!!! [/center]
